data.description: HOME SWEET HOME!!!!  Welcome to the wonderful subdivision "Fern Creek", that is convenient to everything from grocery shopping or fun times at the splash pad!!!  This beautiful home has so much such as the beautiful hardwood floors throughout, the very spacious Great Room with the gas log fire place to stay cozy in the winter right next to the large eat-in kitchen which makes it easy and fun to entertain family and friends.  The large Master Bedroom is plenty big enough for large furniture and the private Master Bath has separate vanities, along with separate garden tub and shower, and a huge walk in closet.  Then let'g go upstairs and where the 2 other good size bedrooms, another 4th Bedroom/Bonus/Playroom/Office,  and a full bath is located.  Plenty of storage in the Walk-in attic.  POURED CONCRETE WALLS in the completely unfinished basement, that is partially finished and would take much for future expansion.  Not to forget the HUGE Fenced in yard also sitting on a full acre lot!!!
